description:
In 2015, the legendary pianist and NEA Jazz Master Dick Hyman sat down with pianist and leading Ragtime scholar Terry Waldo for a discussion of his extraordinary life in music!

Learn more by visiting the Jazz Academy at http://academy.jazz.org

Dick Hyman - Piano
Terry Waldo - Piano
Eric Suquet - Director
Bill Thomas - Director of Photography
Aaron Chandler - Sound Engineer
Seton Hawkins - Producer
